title: Why Your Diet Brain Isn't Broken
itunes:title: Why Your Diet Brain Isn't Broken
description:
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
 
Did you know it's not too late to think knew thoughts? If you've spent a lifetime thinking "I'm so broken" or "I'll never get this" or "I'm just destined to be fat, then listen up.
 
In today's podcast we geek out a little on the brain science. We talk about how the latest science is that we CAN re-program our brains. It just takes practice and patience to believe new things.
